ActCanada Not-for-profit Corporations Act
SubjectOrder Fixing the Day after the Day on which the Order is Made as the Date of the Coming into Force of Certain Sections of the Act
PrecisOrder fixing the day after the day on which this Order is made as the day on which certain provisions of the Act come into force. Those provisions repeal certain provisions of the Canada Corporations Act once all the bodies corporate subject to Part IV of the Act have continued into the Canada Business Corporations Act or have been dissolved, and make consequential amendments to other federal Acts.
